  <brief_title>Serum Bupivacaine Concentration Levels After Injection of Liposomal Bupivacaine Into the Knee</brief_title>
  <official_title>Serum Bupivacaine Concentration Levels After Injection of the Knee Joint With a Mixture of Liposomal Bupivacaine and Free Bupivacaine During Total Knee Arthroplasty</official_title>
